  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/dff6bfcbe71a774ac4dd5a7d11b97b90.poster.avif?t=1727186164\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/dff6bfcbe71a774ac4dd5a7d11b97b90.webm?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/dff6bfcbe71a774ac4dd5a7d11b97b90.mp4?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCustom-made fighting engine with unique moves for each character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tFight with swords, nunchakus, and bo staffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tEngaging story told with carefully crafted pixel-art cut-scenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Dramatic electro soundtrack by Brassica and the Miller bros.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tMany different enemies, each with their own moveset and weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tIntense boss battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tArcade mode for those who want to jump straight into the action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tParry any attacks, projectiles, and traps!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tUpload your high scores and compete globally with other players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tDiscover many secrets and hidden areas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•       Play together in a <strong>local co-op mode</strong>, and heal each other to achieve victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/f283033293009288efdc314ed3bf227d.poster.avif?t=1727186164\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/f283033293009288efdc314ed3bf227d.webm?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/f283033293009288efdc314ed3bf227d.mp4?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SUMMARY:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Black Mantis clan has come to Okinawa... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of the martial arts master Hiro, Meilin, or Shin as they face off in a desperate fight for their lives against the Black Mantis clan. DOUBLE THE MAYHEM: Bring a friend and battle against ninjas, demons, and more in the 2-player local co-op mode of this action-adventure platformer set in a mystical, fantasy version of Okinawa. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fast, fluid combat system brings with it many moves, combos, juggles, and an intuitive parrying system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight to gain the top spot on our online scoreboard! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/53cae2ed6d7a93b823adae2a0fbda612.poster.avif?t=1727186164\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/53cae2ed6d7a93b823adae2a0fbda612.webm?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/53cae2ed6d7a93b823adae2a0fbda612.mp4?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮🕹️ Controls disclaimer: 🕹️🎮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Player: keyboard (not mappable) or pad (you can change controls)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Players: controllers recommended! No support for two players on same keyboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/5cc0568600a3489d8ae4d2588fa0deff.avif?t=1727186164\" width=616 height=213 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/dff6bfcbe71a774ac4dd5a7d11b97b90.poster.avif?t=1727186164\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/dff6bfcbe71a774ac4dd5a7d11b97b90.webm?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/dff6bfcbe71a774ac4dd5a7d11b97b90.mp4?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCustom-made fighting engine with unique moves for each character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tFight with swords, nunchakus, and bo staffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tEngaging story told with carefully crafted pixel-art cut-scenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Dramatic electro soundtrack by Brassica and the Miller bros.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tMany different enemies, each with their own moveset and weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tIntense boss battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tArcade mode for those who want to jump straight into the action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tParry any attacks, projectiles, and traps!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tUpload your high scores and compete globally with other players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tDiscover many secrets and hidden areas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•       Play together in a <strong>local co-op mode</strong>, and heal each other to achieve victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/f283033293009288efdc314ed3bf227d.poster.avif?t=1727186164\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/f283033293009288efdc314ed3bf227d.webm?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/f283033293009288efdc314ed3bf227d.mp4?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SUMMARY:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Black Mantis clan has come to Okinawa... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of the martial arts master Hiro, Meilin, or Shin as they face off in a desperate fight for their lives against the Black Mantis clan. DOUBLE THE MAYHEM: Bring a friend and battle against ninjas, demons, and more in the 2-player local co-op mode of this action-adventure platformer set in a mystical, fantasy version of Okinawa. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fast, fluid combat system brings with it many moves, combos, juggles, and an intuitive parrying system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight to gain the top spot on our online scoreboard! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/53cae2ed6d7a93b823adae2a0fbda612.poster.avif?t=1727186164\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/53cae2ed6d7a93b823adae2a0fbda612.webm?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/53cae2ed6d7a93b823adae2a0fbda612.mp4?t=1727186164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮🕹️ Controls disclaimer: 🕹️🎮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Player: keyboard (not mappable) or pad (you can change controls)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Players: controllers recommended! No support for two players on same keyboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777670/extras/5cc0568600a3489d8ae4d2588fa0deff.avif?t=1727186164\" width=616 height=213 /></span></p>",
